Bank Loan Profile?


       The top three loan types in Bessemer Trust Company, National Association’s loan portfolio are Commercial and Industrial Loans, 1-4 Family Residential Loans, and Multifamily Mortgages.
   
Compared to other banks in New York, Bessemer Trust Company, National Association has a significantly higher percent of Commercial and Industrial Loans on its balance sheet, potentially indicating a specialty in that lending area.


